Author: bumandu
Text: Thank you so much! I just don't want him to get tired of me because of this, I don't want to be a heavy responsibility, but I know it's just my mind playing games with me.  You are so kind, thank you!❤️

Author: alwaystheintern
Text: He can only go as far as you let him baby. I know it’s hard but you are very very lucky to have someone look after you and your health. Much love❤️
